Text: Civil War Weekend Cc Hello there fellow Fraters I m just wishing you all the best on this weekends Civil War I hope to see and speak with as many of you as possible this weekend whether at the game or at good old Clodfelters As for the Alumni donation I guess we are almost there If you havent given but have been considering it let Dustin or I Rich T know If you havent considered it yet then maybe you could start Thank you for your time and Go Beavs Rich Roskopf
